{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_03_01",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、{user}さん\nちょっと聞きたいことがあるんですけど、いいですか",
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。なんでしょう",
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、そこの角で、すずとすれ違ったんですけど\n一人で歌ってて、ぶつかっても気付きもしませんでした",
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "かと思えば、昨日、琴乃を見かけた時は\nなんか暗い感じで俯いたまま歩いてましたし",
      "startTime": 21.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "生え抜きの子達が揃って様子が変なんです\nここの事務所、何かあったんですか？",
      "startTime": 28.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今度、NEXT VENUSグランプリの\n歴代優勝者を集めた祭典に出ることになりまして",
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピで、麻奈の曲をカバーするので\nみんな気合いが入ったり、思うところがあったりで……",
      "startTime": 40.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……ああ、長瀬麻奈\n確かmihoが執念燃やしてた、あの人ですよね",
      "startTime": 49.6333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.4666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "で、今度はみんなで彼女の曲をカバーする、と\n私よく知らないんですけど、そんなに凄かったんですか",
      "startTime": 57.9666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "結構前の人気アイドルってことは分かるんですけど\nその頃はアイドルに興味なかったので覚えてなくて",
      "startTime": 66.0000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5000022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は……琴乃の姉なのはさすがにご存じですよね\nあの頃は、テレビやライブにも引っ張りだこでしたし",
      "startTime": 74.8333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワ……莉央さんと葵の二人と並んで\nグランプリ決勝に進んだ実力者でしたよ",
      "startTime": 82.1666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2000022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリって\n確かアイドルの新人賞でしたっけ",
      "startTime": 88.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そこで月ストとサニピは優勝したんですよね？",
      "startTime": 91.1000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.5000022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "なら、いちいち他人のカバーをしなくても\n自分達の持ち歌を歌えば良さそうなものですけど",
      "startTime": 98.8666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.4333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、いろいろとありまして……",
      "startTime": 102.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんは麻奈にこだわってたけど）\n（スリクスでも、franさんは温度差があるなぁ……）",
      "startTime": 107.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 112.6500022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です……って、なんだか\nいつもにも増してスーツがくたびれてませんか？",
      "startTime": 118.8333356221,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 113.7000022888
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。例の祭典が近づいてきたので\n俺もやることが増えてしまって……",
      "startTime": 126.3333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、大変ですね\nそう言えば、長瀬麻奈のこと少し調べてみました",
      "startTime": 131.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私も今はトップクラスのアイドルですし？\n元同業者のこと知らないのも恥ずかしいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 141.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、当時出てた長瀬麻奈のグッズ\n今でも結構、いい値段がついてるんですよね",
      "startTime": 148.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どう聞いても、興味があるのは値段の方ですよね！？",
      "startTime": 152.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "この間、事務所の倉庫に入る機会があったんですけど\n長瀬麻奈グッズもまだ残ってましたね",
      "startTime": 159.2333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "もし何かあって、星見プロが大赤字になっても\nあれ売ったら少しはしのげますね、良かった良かった",
      "startTime": 166.6000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの一社員として\nそんな日がこないよう、誠心誠意努力いたします……",
      "startTime": 173.2666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしかしたら\nmihoも、長瀬麻奈グッズ持ってるかも",
      "startTime": 179.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "持ってますかね？　……その、mihoさんは\n麻奈のことがあまり好きではないようなので……",
      "startTime": 186.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "嫌いだからなおさら、持ってそうじゃありません？\nほら、研究のためだとか言って",
      "startTime": 193.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、もしかしたら、グッズに五寸釘を打ち込むとか\nそういう用途かもしれませんけど",
      "startTime": 201.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、持っててもうじうじするだけですし\nなら、ぱーっとお金に換えちゃった方がいいですよね",
      "startTime": 207.3000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "今度、聞いてみようっと\nうまいこと言えば、タダでくれるかもしれませんし",
      "startTime": 213.5666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに五寸釘よりは、そのお金で一緒に\n美味しい物でも食べた方がいいかもしれませんね……",
      "startTime": 220.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
